    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a comprehensive service history, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis integrity is verified with documented subframe reinforcement. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with zero bushing deflection, and the engine maintains a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Finished in original paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turn-key, collector-grade example of Bavarian engineering at its zenith.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
