      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and permanent climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or rattles. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history exclusively from authorized dealerships and all preventative maintenance completed ahead of schedule. Every button, sensor, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that satisfies even the most discerning collector's standards.",
