    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and is totally ready for its next big adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been genuinely loved and meticulously cared for, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
