      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing a pristine S54B32 power plant with a flawless VANOS system and reinforced subframe. This example retains its factory-honed mechanical tolerances, featuring the sought-after Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock with optimal engagement. The chassis remains rigid, free of any fatigue, while the suspension geometry is strictly stock, preserving the nuanced feedback of the M-tuned rack-and-pinion steering. Every fluid service has been performed proactively, ensuring the high-compression, individual throttle body induction remains razor-sharp. A true survivor for the discerning collector.",
